Name: MG Battery State of Charge RAW
MG Battery State of Charge
"Equation": LOOKUP(1.1*(VAL{MG Battery State of Charge RAW}+VAL{XX_BMS_Version_SoC _Factor})::-10~0=0:100~110=100)

Name: MG BMS CMU01 Voltage Imbalance
"Equation": (VAL{MG BMS CMU01 MaxVolt} - VAL{MG BMS CMU01 MinVolt}) * 1000

Name: MG BMS CMU02 Voltage Imbalance
"Equation": (VAL{MG BMS CMU02 MaxVolt} - VAL{MG BMS CMU02 MinVolt}) * 1000

Name: MG BMS CMU03 Voltage Imbalance
"Equation": (VAL{MG BMS CMU03 MaxVolt} - VAL{MG BMS CMU03 MinVolt}) * 1000

"Equation": (VAL{MG BMS CMU04 MaxVolt} - VAL{MG BMS CMU04 MinVolt}) * 1000

Name: MG BMS CMU05 Voltage Imbalance
"Equation": (VAL{MG BMS CMU05 MaxVolt} - VAL{MG BMS CMU05 MinVolt}) * 1000

Name: MG BMS CMU06 Voltage Imbalance
"Equation": (VAL{MG BMS CMU06 MaxVolt} - VAL{MG BMS CMU06 MinVolt}) * 1000

Name: MG BMS CMU07 Voltage Imbalance
"Equation": (VAL{MG BMS CMU07 MaxVolt} - VAL{MG BMS CMU07 MinVolt}) * 1000

"Equation": (VAL{MG BMS CMU08 MaxVolt} - VAL{MG BMS CMU08 MinVolt}) * 1000

Name: MG BMS CMU09 Voltage Imbalance
"Equation": (VAL{MG BMS CMU09 MaxVolt} - VAL{MG BMS CMU09 MinVolt}) * 1000

Name: MG BMS CMU Overall Imbalance
"Equation": (VAL{MG BMS CMU01 Voltage Imbalance}+VAL{MG BMS CMU02 Voltage Imbalance}+VAL{MG BMS CMU03 Voltage Imbalance}+VAL{MG BMS CMU04 Voltage Imbalance}+VAL{MG BMS CMU05 Voltage Imbalance}+VAL{MG BMS CMU06 Voltage Imbalance}+VAL{MG BMS CMU07 Voltage Imbalance}+VAL{MG BMS CMU08 Voltage Imbalance}+VAL{MG BMS CMU09 Voltage Imbalance})/9

Name: MG4EV_Range_60MPH
"Equation": (42*VAL{MG4EV_Cons_60MPH})*(1-((25-VAL{XX_OAT_Factored})/100))*(VAL{MG Battery State of Charge}/100)*(VAL{MG Battery State of Health}/100)

Name: MG4EV_Range_70MPH
"Equation": (42*VAL{XX_Cons_70MPH})*(1-((25-VAL{XX_OAT_Factored})/100))*(VAL{MG Battery State of Charge}/100)*(VAL{MG Battery State of Health}/100)
